{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1782183915130,"sessionID":"ses_10d8fdd23ffe7jQGDNRfH10rBw","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"796465679","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Cache API\n\nExported from `cache.mjs` in the [`cache.mjs`](cache.mjs).\n\n## createCache()\n\nCreates a cache instance with `get`, `set`, `delete`, and `clear` methods.\n\n### Usage\n\n```js\nimport { createCache } from './cache.mjs'\n\nconst cache = createCache()\n```\n\n### Methods\n\nThe returned object has the following methods:\n\n#### get(key)\n\nRetrieves a value from the cache by key.\n\n```js\ncache.get(key) // returns value or undefined\n```\n\n#### set(key, value)\n\nSets a value in the cache by key and returns the value.\n\n```js\ncache.set(key, value) // returns value\n```\n\n#### delete(key)\n\nDeletes a value from the cache by key and returns `true` if the key existed, `false` otherwise.\n\n```js\ncache.delete(key) // returns true or false\n```\n\n#### clear()\n\nClears all entries from the cache.\n\n```js\ncache.clear()\n```\n\nThe cache uses an in-memory `Map` to store values.\n","filePath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-22T19-55-04-956Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-3/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/private/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-22T19-55-04-956Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-3/repo/bench-artifacts/cache-api.md","exists":false,"truncated":false,"tokenwarden":{"wouldHaveUsedTokens":6,"usedTokens":6,"savedTokens":0,"percentSaved":0,"rawPath":"/tmp/tokenwarden-bench/2026-06-22T19-55-04-956Z/tokenwarden-docs-from-code-3/tokenwarden/encrypted/raw-tool-output/ses_10d8fdd23ffe7jQGDNRfH10rBw/796465679.txt.enc","event":{"timestamp":"2026-06-23T03:05:15.112Z","sessionID":"ses_10d8fdd23ffe7jQGDNRfH10rBw","source":"tool-output","label":"write","wouldHaveUsedTokens":6,"usedTokens":6,"savedTokens":0,"percentSaved":0,"metadata":{"callID":"796465679","rawPath":"/tmp/tokenwarde